===Entrances=== 

*No-clipping through a pink wall in [[Level 996]].
*One can enter '''Level 986''' by staring at something pink for too long in [[Level List|any level]].
*Following a sign reading "MILLER" on [[Level 948]].
*Drinking contaminated water on the Guts of [[Level 989]].
*Staying completely still in [[Level 917]].

===Exits ===

*No-clipping through a white wall will take one to [[Level 996]].
*No-clipping into strong and bright lights will take one to [[Level 917]].
*Drawing something deemed creative on the papers on cells will take one to [[Level 974]].
*Walking far enough will take one to [[Level 988]].
*Jumping out of a window may take one to [[Level 993]] or [[Level 993.1]].
*Occasionally, one may spot a tunnel within this level, walking through it will lead one to [[Level 987]] or [[Level 990]].
*Falling asleep may lead one to [[Level 233]].
*Noclipping while in a group of 4 wanderers or less has a high chance for the whole group to be taken to [[Level 911]].
